data.description: $2K Buyer Allowance for 3rd Floor Carpet or Closing Costs! Amazing opportunity to own this beautiful 3BR/3.5BA townhome in Enclave at Grant Park!! Originally used as the model townhome when the subdivision was developed, this amazing home happily awaits it's next owner. You will enjoy all that this home has to offer: Elegant owner's suite with trey ceilings and a 2nd en suite bedroom on top level, 3rd en suite bedroom on the lower level, living room with cozy fireplace, stainless steel appliances, deck, covered patio, balcony, and a 1 car attached garage. The home also allows for ample natural light exposure to brighten up your day. The seller has recently updated several important items to the townhome, including a new roof, newer HVAC systems, and toilets. This is a very quiet neighborhood with an active HOA that takes great pride in maintaining the community. This community offers plenty of green space, a dog walk, and exceptionally low HOA fees. Excellent location with easy access to the Beltline, Grant Park, Grants Park Farmer's Market, Zoo Atlanta, restaurants, and shopping. Conveniently accessible to I-20 & I-75/85 highways, and to Atlanta's finest higher education centers: Emory University, Georgia State University, Georgia Tech, and the AUC Center. $1,000 Lender Credit Offered By Preferred Lender. You do not want to miss out on this one! Agents, please see Private Remarks.
